<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Wander on 贤民的博客</title><link>https://www.xianmin.org/categories/wander/</link><description>Recent content in Wander on 贤民的博客</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Oct 2022 22:15:10 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.xianmin.org/categories/wander/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>兼职领队 - 香格里拉无底湖露营徒步</title><link>https://www.xianmin.org/post/2022/09-part-time-outdoor-tour-leader/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Oct 2022 22:15:10 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.xianmin.org/post/2022/09-part-time-outdoor-tour-leader/</guid><description>&lt;p>十一休假，经朋友推荐，我到某某户外俱乐部做了回兼职领队。以前在青旅，我也经常带队组织户外活动，但规模小、也并非自己的主业，有些业余。这次做兼职领队的主要目的， &lt;strong>是想了解专业的户外俱乐部是怎样组织活动的、整个活动的流程、以及专业领队在活动中具体的工作内容&lt;/strong> 。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>十月是登山的季节</title><link>https://www.xianmin.org/post/review-2019-10/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2019 06:55:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.xianmin.org/post/review-2019-10/</guid><description>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.xianmin.org/css/hugo-easy-gallery.css" />
